title: Zoom Organic
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Pizza, Organic, Western, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Organic market and cafe. Offers vegan choices in salads, at least 1 soup, 1 curry, and vegan pizza. Many cakes and biscuits are vegan and labeled as such. Makes toasted sandwiches, has vegan and vegetarian pies, smoothies and juices. Sells a range of healthy lifestyle products including organic cosmetics and essential oils.
